media:group.media:title: Are cheap laser cutters safe?
media:group.media:description:
Laser cutters are incredibly handy tools, but the technology poses a significant safety risk... and these companies don't seem to care!
In this video I'll run you through all of these risks, and how to manage them so you can use laser cutters to make awesome things!
Makerspace Laser Cutter Safety - https://youtu.be/uZ6U1lTSD_Q

entry.title: 3D Print your own mini battlebot! (FULL tutorial FREE .stl download)

media:group.media:title: 3D Print your own mini battlebot! (FULL tutorial FREE .stl download)
media:group.media:description:
Learn how to design, print and build your very own combat robot (battlebot)!
In this detailed tutorial you'll learn how to create an antweight (150g) controlled fighting machine using low cost parts and a 3D Printer!
You can use this tutorial to create almost any remote controlled robot platform of any size. If you create something, please let me know!!!
.STL and .STEP downloads - https://www.makersmuse.com/3d-printed-antweight-v1
Learning Resources: Robowars Adelaide event - https://www.sciencealive.net.au/ Lipo battery disposal - https://hobbyking.com/en_us/blog/lipo-battery-disposal-for-beginners/ LED resistor calculator - https://www.allaboutcircuits.com/tools/led-resistor-calculator/
Part Resources (FEEL FREE TO USE YOUR OWN - MAY BECOME UNAVAILABLE) Gearmotors - https://www.ebay.com.au/itm/192569276688 Battery - https://hobbyking.com/en_us/turnigy-nano-tech-300mah-2s-35-70c-lipo-pack.html Flipsky dual ESC (DOES NOT HAVE MOTOR BRAKE) - https://flipsky.net/collections/electronic-products/products/brushed-esc-dual-way-speed-controller-2s-3s-5ax2-esc-speed-control-for-rc-vehicle-car-boat-tank-airplane-fixed-wing-drone
More to come.
